    "The figure is sourced from[254] Fig. 33 (33Fig.",
    "33 (Color online) Sketch of the QCD phase diagram.",
    "The dashed line represents the smooth crossover region up to B ∕T ≤ 3.",
    "The black solid line represents the speculated first-order phase boundary.",
    "The empirical thermal freeze-out results from global hadron yield data are shown as the red-yellow line [53]."
